  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. Expanding gives 8<i>x</i> &minus; 40 = &minus;2<i>x</i> &minus; 40. Adding 2<i>x</i> + 40 to both sides yields 10<i>x</i> = 0, so <i>x</i> = 0 is the unique solution.</p><p>Choice A would require a contradiction, choice D would require an identity, and choice C is impossible for a linear equation.</p>",
